'''Jonathan Cook''' provided the voice for [[Sev/Legends|Sev]] in ''[[Star Wars: Republic Commando]]''. He also provided some minor voices for ''[[Star Wars: Battlefront II]]''. He is known in the game as the one with the low voice and his rough sense of humor.

